Introduction

In given data set we will make an Extrapolatory Data Analysis.

We will answer following questions:

What are the values in given dataset? What are the distributions? Are there relationships? Where?

What kind of data types?(continuous/discreet/categorical)

Identify outliers Goal of 1st part of project:graphical displays of data and numerical summaries of data
